text: Émile Fréteur (22 May 1879 - 14 June 1953) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1879 births Category:1953 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:People from Croix, Nord
